            our output         expected

"$"USER""   seg fault          $USER: command not found
$"$USER"    $USER              rpaic
$           OK? - META_DOL     becames $ as cmd  
'$USER'     null               $USER: command not found
"'$USER'"   seg fault          'rpaic': command not found
"$USER"     sega               rpaic: command not found

cat | ls    working on         fa' "ls" poi "cat" aspetta un input, 
                               appena lo riceve fa exit 0: command not found

cat | cat | cat | ls           fa "ls" poi ogni cat aspetta un input.
                               dopo 3 input fa exit 0

